Class CustomerEditScreenController

java.lang.Object
controller.CustomerEditScreenController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class CustomerEditScreenController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller class that controls the logic of the customer edit screen that is calls when the user add new or modify a appointment from the Customer screen of the application.
